{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"includeOptional","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" = true) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Hashable","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"tag","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value to use as the view’s tag.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"includeOptional","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the tag value for ","type":"text"},{"code":"Optional<V>","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"also be set.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view with the specified tag set."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to differentiate among certain selectable views,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"like the possible values of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"text":" or the tabs of a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TabView"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Tag values can be of any type that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/hashable","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This modifier will write the tag value for the type "},{"code":"V","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", as well as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"Optional<V>","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if "},{"code":"includeOptional","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled. Containers checking for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags of either type will see the value as set."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the example below, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" loop in the "},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"builder iterates over the "},{"code":"Flavor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" enumeration. It extracts the string"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of each enumeration element for use in constructing the row"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"label, and uses the enumeration value as input to the "},{"code":"tag(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifier."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct FlavorPicker: View {","    enum Flavor: String, CaseIterable, Identifiable {","        case chocolate, vanilla, strawberry","        var id: Self { self }","    }","","    @State private var selectedFlavor: Flavor? = nil","","    var body: some View {","        Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","            ForEach(Flavor.allCases) { flavor in","                Text(flavor.rawValue)","                    .tag(flavor)","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The selection type of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<Flavor>"},{"type":"text","text":" and so it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will look for tags on its contents of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Optional<Flavor>"},{"type":"text","text":"type. Since the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tag modifier defaults to having "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"includeOptional"},{"type":"text","text":" enabled, even though"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the tag for each option is a non-optional "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Flavor"},{"type":"text","text":", the tag modifier"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"writes values for both the non-optional, and optional versions of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value, allowing the contents to be selectable by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ForEach","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" automatically applies a default tag to each enumerated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter of the corresponding element. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the element’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"id"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter and the picker’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"selection"},{"type":"text","text":" input"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have exactly the same type, or the same type but optional, you can omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the explicit tag modifier."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To see examples that don’t require an explicit tag, see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/labeledcontent\/tag(_:includeoptional:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContent\/tag(_:includeOptional:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContent"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tag","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"includeOptional","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"tag(_:includeOptional:)","remoteSource":{"fileName":"Tag.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/View\/Tag.swift#L71"}